de.unifrankfurt.informatik.dbis.dia.config

Class Config

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.unifrankfurt.informatik.dbis.dia.config.Config

  • public class Config
extends java.lang.Object
    The config for the QueryManager, ResultManager and the the whole rest. The Config holds the entire information about the Entity-, as well as about the Filter-class.

    These are:

    • sourceField: The name of the field in that the source-id is injected.
    • varMapping: A Map<String, EntityConfigElement> which maps the variable to a entity config.
    • helpVarMapping: A Map<String, EntityConfigElement> which maps the non-mapped variable to a entity config.
    • filterMapping: A Map<String, FilterConfigElement> which maps the filter Field to a filter config.
